"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pentagon has confirmed that a US submarine sank an Iranian warship in the Indian Ocean. This incident adds to the tensions in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Submarine Sinks Iranian Warship\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Pent\u00e1gono confirm\u00f3 que un submarino de EE.UU. hundi\u00f3 un barco de guerra iran\u00ed en el Oc\u00e9ano \u00cdndico. Este incidente aumenta las tensiones en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Submarino de EE.UU. hunde barco iran\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Civilians are being displaced as Israel retaliates to Hezbollah rocket attacks. People are taking shelter in tents, parks, and cars due to the conflict.\",            \"english_title\": \"Civilians Displaced in Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los civiles est\u00e1n siendo desplazados mientras Israel responde a los ataques con cohetes de Hezbollah. La gente se refugia en tiendas, parques y coches por el conflicto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Civiles desplazados en conflicto\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Sri Lanka's navy reports that around 140 people are feared missing after a military vessel sank off its southern coast. Rescue operations are ongoing.\",            \"english_title\": \"Sri Lanka Vessel Sinks\",            \"translated_version\": \"La marina de Sri Lanka informa que se teme que unas 140 personas est\u00e9n desaparecidas despu\u00e9s de que un barco militar se hundiera en su costa sur. Las operaciones de rescate contin\u00faan.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Barco de Sri Lanka se hunde\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Spain's prime minister has responded strongly to US President Donald Trump's threat to end trade with Spain. The prime minister emphasized the importance of maintaining trade relations.\",            \"english_title\": \"Spain Responds to US Trade Threat\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de Espa\u00f1a respondi\u00f3 fuertemente a la amenaza del presidente de EE.UU., Donald Trump, de terminar el comercio con Espa\u00f1a. El primer ministro enfatiz\u00f3 la importancia de mantener relaciones comerciales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Espa\u00f1a responde a amenaza comercial de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US soldiers were killed when a drone evaded air defenses and hit a command center in Port Shuaiba, Kuwait. This attack highlights the ongoing risks in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attack in Kuwait\",            \"translated_version\": \"Soldados de EE.UU. murieron cuando un dron evadi\u00f3 las defensas a\u00e9reas y golpe\u00f3 un centro de mando en el Puerto Shuaiba, Kuwait. Este ataque resalta los riesgos continuos en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de dron en Kuwait\"        }    ]}"